$AV_ZETRFCY
If clalev([F:FCY])=0 : Local File FACILITY [FCY] : Endif
Call LECTURE("FCY",num$([M]ETRFCY(indice)),"") From CONTOBJ
zc = [F:FCY]FCYNAM
Gosub _AFF
Return

